    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the one you've been waiting for \u2014 a stunning example of automotive passion preserved in time. Slide behind the wheel and feel the story unfold: a cabin that whispers of open highways and weekend adventures yet to come, bodywork that catches the light like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail speaks to a life well-lived but carefully tended, a machine that has been cherished rather than merely used. Whether you're cruising the coast or turning heads in the city, this beauty is ready to become the centerpiece of your driving life. Opportunities like this don't linger \u2014 they belong to those bold enough to seize them.",
      "price": 43000.0,
